---
import Layout from "../components/Layout.astro";
import Heading from "../components/Heading.astro";
---

<Layout title="关于 — 张大强的博客" description="关于我和这个博客">
  <script slot="head" type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify({
    "@context": "https://schema.org",
    "@type": "AboutPage",
    "name": "关于张大强的博客",
    "description": "关于我和这个博客",
    "url": Astro.site?.href + "about/",
    "mainEntity": {
      "@type": "Person",
      "name": "张大强",
      "url": Astro.site?.href,
    },
  })} />

  <article class="prose">
    <Heading as="h1">关于</Heading>

    <p>这里是张大强的博客，记录技术探索、工具折腾和生活思考。</p>

    <p>一个喜欢折腾技术的开发者，从 Hugo 到 Halo 再到 Astro，博客平台换了一轮又一轮，不变的是一直在写。</p>

    <p>使用 <a href="https://astro.build/">Astro</a> + <a href="https://github.com/Get-UINUX/uinux-blog">UINUX Blog</a> 主题构建，部署在 <a href="https://pages.cloudflare.com/">Cloudflare Pages</a> 上。</p>

    <h2>联系我</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>GitHub: <a href="https://github.com/dadadaqiang">dadadaqiang</a></li>
    </ul>
  </article>
</Layout>
